# Tech Stack: Arthur Geron's Portfolio

## Core Technologies
- **UI Framework:** SolidJS (v1.9.5)
- **Bundler:** Rspack (v1.2.8)
- **Runtime & Package Manager:** Bun (v1.2.6)
- **Language:** TypeScript (v5.8.2)
- **Node Version:** 23.10.0 (as specified in .tool-versions)

## Key Libraries & Dependencies
- **Routing:** `@solidjs/router` (v0.15.3)
- **Data Fetching:** `@tanstack/solid-query` (v5.69.0)
- **Animation:**
  - GSAP (v3.12.7) with ScrollTrigger plugin
  - Motion One for Solid (`@motionone/solid` v10.16.4)
  - `split-type` (v0.3.4) for text animations

## Styling
- **CSS Framework:** TailwindCSS (v3.4.1)
- **Component Library:** DaisyUI (v5.0.9)
- **Post-processing:** PostCSS (v8.4.35) with Autoprefixer (v10.4.21)

## Development Tooling
- **Linting & Formatting:** Biome (v1.9.4)
- **Hot Module Replacement:** solid-refresh (v0.7.5)
- **Environment Management:** cross-env
- **Babel:** babel-preset-solid & babel-loader for SolidJS JSX transformation

## Configuration Files
- `rspack.config.ts` - Bundler configuration
- `tsconfig.json` - TypeScript compiler options
- `biome.json` - Linting and formatting rules
- `tailwind.config.js` - Styling theme and utilities
- `postcss.config.js` - CSS processing pipeline
- `.babelrc` - Babel configuration for SolidJS 